0)==========History=============================

Updated: 05.05.05
Current:
  - Problem with Sector bend accuracy
  - Problem with Magnetic field in BDSElement




1)==========Installation instructions============

You will need Geant4 and Root installed before compiling

to compile:

    ./configure
    make

to run:

    bdsim [options]

to run without Geant4 interactive propmt:

    bdsim --batch 

Quit Geant4 session with  'exit' to save the Root file

2)==========Other files========================

BDS_vis.mac      : sample G4 visualization script
test.gmad

3)==========Directories===================

parser/          : gmad parser
examples/        : sample lettices
utils/           : various useful scripts
